# SKAdNetworkIdentifier

**Property List Key**

A string that contains an ad network ID.

## Discussion

Contact the ad network to learn their ad network ID. Include this key, and the value of the ad network ID as a string, as a dictionary in the [doc://com.apple.bundleresources/documentation/BundleResources/Information-Property-List/SKAdNetworkItems] key.
